<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome</title>

    <style>
        .content {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #F2F2F2;
        }
        .header {
            margin: 0px 48px 0px 48px;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .header-logo {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 32px 0px 24px 0px;
        }

        .header-logo img {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
        }

        .header-text {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px;
            color: #2D363D;
        }
            .header > img {
                width: 20px;
                height: 20px;
            }

        .header-text .title {
            padding-bottom: 7px;
        }

        .middle {
            border: 1px solid #DADAEB;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            max-width: 568px;
            margin: 0px 16px 0px 16px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .yellow-border {
            border: 1px solid #FFD201;
        }

        .content-box {
            max-width: 504px;
            margin: 24px 32px 32px 32px;
        }

        .middle-logo {
            margin: 0px 0px 16px 0px;
        }

        img {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
        }

        .rectangle {
            background: #DADAEB;
            max-width: 504px;
            height: 1px;
            margin: 0px 48px 0px 48px;
        }

        .rectangle-middle {
            margin: 0px 32px 0px 32px;
        }

        .rectangle-box {
            max-width: 568px;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #DADAEB;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .middle-text {
            padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            color: #2D363D;
        }

        .title {
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .bottom {
            max-width: 568px;
            margin: 24px 16px 0px 16px;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .button-rectangle {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 56px;
            background: #1CD18B;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .button-rectangle img {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }

        .person {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 0px 16px 32px;
        }

        .arrow {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 32px 16px 0px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .text {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top:14px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .bottom-text {
            max-width: 504px;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            margin: 16px 32px 0px 32px;
            padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px;
            color: #2D363D;
        }

        .footer {
            max-width: 568px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 16px 0px 16px;
            padding-bottom: 31px;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            color: #9999AD;
        }

            .footer img {
                width: 10px;
                height: 10px;

            }

        .footer .text-box {
            max-width: 504px;
            margin: 0px 32px 0px 32px;
        }

        .text-box .big {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px;
            color: #9999AD;
        }

        .text-box .general {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .small-font {
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        .medium-font-14 {
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .medium-font-16 {
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: bold;
            line-height: 22px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .title-font {
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: 22px;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;

        }

        .green {
            color: #1CD18B;
        }

        .text-box-general {
            max-width: 504px;
            margin: 24px 48px 32px 48px;
            color: #2D363D;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 0px !important;
        }

    </style>

</head>
<body>

<div class="content">

    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-logo">
            <img src="{{ logo }}" alt="Frizbee Logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="header-text medium-font-14">
            <div class="title title-font bold green">
                Thank you for joining our ranks!
            </div>
            <div>
                You are now an official resident of Frizbee, the global community of people connected by their passions.
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="middle yellow-border">

        <div class="content-box">
            <div class="middle-logo">
                <img src="{{ wallet_attention }}" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="middle-text small-font">
                Your new account is associated with your unique wallet file (attached to this message), password and seed phrase. We strongly recommend that you keep all of these safe, to make sure you never get locked out of your account and wallet. <br />
                Please remember we do not store any of this information and cannot assist you in the event of lost access.
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="text-box-general small-font">
        Don’t let the good times wait - go explore the Frizbee app and discover what’s already happening in our hobby hub!
    </div>

    <div class="middle">

        <div class="content-box">
            <div class="middle-logo">
                <img src="{{ compass }}" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="middle-text" style="letter-spacing: unset;">
                <div class="title title-font regular">
                    Explore the community and join groups already engaging over your preferred hobby
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rectangle rectangle-middle"></div>

        <div class="content-box">
            <div class="middle-logo">
                <img src="{{ dollar }}" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="middle-text" style="letter-spacing: unset;">
                <div class="title title-font regular">
                    Add funds to your Frizbee wallet and get ready to invest in your favorite hobby
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rectangle rectangle-middle"></div>

        <div class="content-box">
            <div class="middle-logo">
                <img src="{{ search }}" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="middle-text" style="letter-spacing: unset;">
                <div class="title title-font regular">
                    Find an inspiring mentor and get started with your first live training session
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="bottom" style="padding-bottom: 0px;">

        <div class="button-rectangle">
            <div class="person">
                <img src="{{ small_compass }}" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="text medium-font-16">
                Explore Frizbee
            </div>
            <div class="arrow">
                <img src="{{ arrow }}" alt="" />
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer" style="margin-top: 16px;">

        <div class="text-box small-font">
            <div class="general">
                We can’t wait to see how Frizbee will make a change in your life, as a teacher, a student or both! <br />
                reCreate your time.
            </div>
            <div class="general signature">
                the Frizbee <img src="{{ heart }}" alt=""  /> Bunch
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>